                    <p><strong>You:</strong> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Quia, eum dolorum quas eligendi, delectus illum veniam expedita voluptatibus corporis beatae dignissimos minima facere? Sed maxime vel, consequatur mollitia rem molestiae.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="message other-message">
                    <p><strong>User 2:</strong> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Earum debitis corporis dolores illum odio soluta ipsa magnam omnis deserunt! Necessitatibus quisquam pariatur numquam voluptates dolor ratione in nobis nulla omnis.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="message other-message">
                    <p><strong>User 2:</strong> And you?</p>
                </div>
                <div class="message my-message">
                    <p><strong>You:</strong> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <input type="text" class="input-message" placeholder="Type a message...">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>